ht search terms and easily understood by all search engines. It identifies different opportunities to refine your content and HTML structure for better visibility, so your site can get found by the right people.<\/p>\n<p>What it checks:<\/p>\n<ul class=\"ticks\">\n<li>Title tags and meta descriptions for length and keyword optimisation.<\/li>\n<li>Proper use of header tags (H1-H6) for clear content hierarchy.<\/li>\n<li>Distribution of target keywords across key elements to boost rankings.<\/li>\n<li>Alt text for images to boost accessibility and image search ranking.<\/li>\n<li>Essential technical SEO elements like canonical tags, hreflang attributes, and structured data.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n                                  <\/div>\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:ml-1\/12 order-first md:order-last\">\n                                      <figure class=\"media\">\n                      <img width=\"642\" height=\"462\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/SEO_Checker_Step2-1.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 576px,(max-width: 768px) 768px,(max-width: 1024px) 1024px,(max-width: 1366px) 1366px,(max-width: 1600px) 1600px,100vw\" \/>                    <\/figure>\n                                  <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                      <div class=\"services-sticky-item\">\n              <div class=\"row justify-center md:flex-nowrap md:gap-12 items-center\">\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:w-4\/12 lg:ml-1\/12 wysiwyg\">\n                                      <h3>Backlinks<\/h3>\n                                                        <p>Backlinks are an important factor in building trust and authority online. Our SEO Checker evaluates your site\u2019s backlink profile to discover what&#8217;s working and what is not.<\/p>\n<p>What it checks:<\/p>\n<ul class=\"ticks\">\n<li>Number and quality of backlinks and referring domains.<\/li>\n<li>Balance between no follow to do follow links.<\/li>\n<li>Anchor text usage and how well it aligns with your keywords.<\/li>\n<li>Top linking pages and where your backlinks are coming from globally.<\/li>\n<li>Link distribution across your site for maximum impact.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n                                  <\/div>\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:ml-1\/12 order-first md:order-last\">\n                                      <figure class=\"media\">\n                      <img width=\"542\" height=\"491\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Backlink_graphic2-1.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 576px,(max-width: 768px) 768px,(max-width: 1024px) 1024px,(max-width: 1366px) 1366px,(max-width: 1600px) 1600px,100vw\" \/>                    <\/figure>\n                                  <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                      <div class=\"services-sticky-item\">\n              <div class=\"row justify-center md:flex-nowrap md:gap-12 items-center\">\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:w-4\/12 lg:ml-1\/12 wysiwyg\">\n                                      <h3>Usability<\/h3>\n                                                        <p>A user-friendly site keeps visitors engaged and reduces bounce rates. Our SEO Checker evaluates your site\u2019s accessibility and functionality across all devices.<\/p>\n<p>What it checks:<\/p>\n<ul class=\"ticks\">\n<li>Mobile responsiveness and viewport settings, because your site should look fantastic whether it&#8217;s on a phone, tablet, or desktop.<\/li>\n<li>Ensures your text is readable and buttons are easy to tap, even on smaller phone screens.<\/li>\n<li>The use of favicons and accessibility practices.<\/li>\n<li>The use of iFrame and making sure navigation is not impacted by any embedded content.<\/li>\n<li>Performance on Google\u2019s Core Web Vitals, for fast loading times and optimal user experience.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n                                  <\/div>\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:ml-1\/12 order-first md:order-last\">\n                                      <figure class=\"media\">\n                      <img width=\"545\" height=\"463\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/SEO_Checker_Step3-1.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 576px,(max-width: 768px) 768px,(max-width: 1024px) 1024px,(max-width: 1366px) 1366px,(max-width: 1600px) 1600px,100vw\" \/>                    <\/figure>\n                                  <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                      <div class=\"services-sticky-item\">\n              <div class=\"row justify-center md:flex-nowrap md:gap-12 items-center\">\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:w-4\/12 lg:ml-1\/12 wysiwyg\">\n                                      <h3>Performance and Load Times<\/h3>\n                                                        <p>Speed is everything. Our SEO Checker helps pinpoint areas where your site could do with an increase in load times and performance, making sure visitors (and search engines) do not have to wait around.<\/p>\n<p>What it checks:<\/p>\n<ul class=\"ticks\">\n<li>Page load times and server response speed.<\/li>\n<li>Image &amp; resource optimisation.<\/li>\n<li>Compression techniques like Gzip or Brotli.<\/li>\n<li>JavaScript errors and unnecessary redirects.<\/li>\n<li>CSS &amp; JavaScript minification.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n                                  <\/div>\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:ml-1\/12 order-first md:order-last\">\n                                      <figure class=\"media\">\n                      <img width=\"654\" height=\"530\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Performance_graphic1-1.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 576px,(max-width: 768px) 768px,(max-width: 1024px) 1024px,(max-width: 1366px) 1366px,(max-width: 1600px) 1600px,100vw\" \/>                    <\/figure>\n                                  <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                      <div class=\"services-sticky-item\">\n              <div class=\"row justify-center md:flex-nowrap md:gap-12 items-center\">\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:w-4\/12 lg:ml-1\/12 wysiwyg\">\n                                      <h3>Social Signals<\/h3>\n                                                        <p>Social media is key for brand visibility and customer engagement. Our SEO Checker analyses your social presence, noting any opportunities to strengthen your online presence.<\/p>\n<p>What it checks:<\/p>\n<ul class=\"ticks\">\n<li>Links to active social media profiles (Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, etc.).<\/li>\n<li>Missing or inactive profiles.<\/li>\n<li>Integration of YouTube channels or other content hubs.<\/li>\n<li>Opportunities to increase visibility and engagement.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n                                  <\/div>\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:ml-1\/12 order-first md:order-last\">\n                                      <figure class=\"media\">\n                      <img width=\"633\" height=\"459\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/SEO_Checker_Step6-1.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 576px,(max-width: 768px) 768px,(max-width: 1024px) 1024px,(max-width: 1366px) 1366px,(max-width: 1600px) 1600px,100vw\" \/>                    <\/figure>\n                                  <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                      <div class=\"services-sticky-item\">\n              <div class=\"row justify-center md:flex-nowrap md:gap-12 items-center\">\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:w-4\/12 lg:ml-1\/12 wysiwyg\">\n                                      <h3>Local SEO<\/h3>\n                                                        <p>Being found in the right searches for local businesses is essential. Our SEO Checker determines how well your site is optimised for local search, making sure you&#8217;re visible when potential customers are looking for you nearby.<\/p>\n<p>What it checks:<\/p>\n<ul class=\"ticks\">\n<li>Completeness of your Google Business Profile, ensuring all your details are filled out and up-to-date.<\/li>\n<li>Local business schema usage, which helps search engines understand your location and services.<\/li>\n<li>Accuracy of business information like address and phone number.<\/li>\n<li>Quantity and quality of Google reviews.<\/li>\n<li>Opportunities to improve local search rankings.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n                                  <\/div>\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:ml-1\/12 order-first md:order-last\">\n                                      <figure class=\"media\">\n                      <img width=\"587\" height=\"484\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/SEO_Checker_Step7-1.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 576px,(max-width: 768px) 768px,(max-width: 1024px) 1024px,(max-width: 1366px) 1366px,(max-width: 1600px) 1600px,100vw\" \/>                    <\/figure>\n                                  <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                      <div class=\"services-sticky-item\">\n              <div class=\"row justify-center md:flex-nowrap md:gap-12 items-center\">\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:w-4\/12 lg:ml-1\/12 wysiwyg\">\n                                      <h3>Site Technology<\/h3>\n                                                        <p>A robust website relies on the right tools and technologies. Our SEO Checker reviews your site&#8217;s backend to ensure it&#8217;s secure and fast.<\/p>\n<p>What it checks:<\/p>\n<ul class=\"ticks\">\n<li>Content management systems (e.g., WordPress), making sure your CMS is up to the task.<\/li>\n<li>Security protocols like HTTPS and DMARC.<\/li>\n<li>Use of modern technologies like HTTP\/3 and caching tools.<\/li>\n<li>Implementation of analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics, Tag Manager), to help you track.<\/li>\n<li>Deprecated HTML tags or inline styles that may impact performance.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n                                  <\/div>\n                <div class=\"w-full md:w-1\/2 lg:ml-1\/12 order-first md:order-last\">\n                                      <figure class=\"media\">\n                      <img width=\"650\" height=\"603\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cbwebsitedesign.co.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/SEO_Checker_Step8-2.svg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 576px) 576px,(max-width: 768px) 768px,(max-width: 1024px) 1024px,(max-width: 1366px) 1366px,(max-width: 1600px) 1600px,100vw\" \/>                    <\/figure>\n                                  <\/div>\n              <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                  <\/div>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n<!-- cost-calc-cta --><section class=\"cost-cal-cta section  padded inverted\">\n  <div class=\"bg bg-padded bg-dark\">\n              <svg\n          class=\"bg-lights absolute left-1\/2 top-1\/2 w-full -translate-x-1\/2 -translate-y-1\/2 rotate-[35deg]\"\n          xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"\n          viewbox=\"0 0 1920 1080\"\n          preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid slice\">\n          <g class=\"lines fill-red opacity-10\">\n            <rect class=\"line\" x=\"1253.6\" width=\"4.5\" heig